questionName: From EVT logs, check which DIi_PitX_EmergencyRun is recorded as true (+) status before pitch emergency run fault recorded?
questionAnswers: One of the input high- DI 88/89/90- DIi_Pit1/2/3_EmergencyRun.
All three digital inputs 88, 89 and 90 DIi_Pit1_EmergencyRun recorded true at the same time.
